@OrderService.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### Get JWT Token
POST {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Create Order (requires token from above)
POST {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "currency": "USD",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_FROM_DB",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Get Order by ID
GET {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/orders/ORDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### List Orders
GET {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Confirm Order
POST {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/orders/ORDER_ID_HERE/confirm
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Idempotency-Key: confirm-unique-key-123

### Cancel Order
POST {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/orders/ORDER_ID_HERE/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Idempotency-Key: cancel-unique-key-456

